sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant App as Changes Webview
participant Router as ChangesMessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as StashWorktreeUseCase
participant StatusUseCase as GetStatusUseCase
participant Worktree as Worktree implements WorktreeOperationCapabilities
participant Runtime as HybridGitRuntime
participant Cli as CliGitRuntime

User->>App: Click Stash
App->>Router: changes/stash(worktreeLocator, message, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveWorktree(worktreeLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Worktree
Router->>UseCase: execute(Worktree, message, signal)
UseCase->>Worktree: stash(message, signal)
Worktree->>Runtime: stash(executionContext, message, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: stash(executionContext, message, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: success
Runtime-->>Worktree: success
Worktree-->>UseCase: success
UseCase-->>Router: success
Router-->>App: changes/stashResponse(requestId)
Router-->>App: changes/refreshRequested

App->>Router: changes/statusRequest(repositoryLocator, worktreeLocator, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveWorktree(worktreeLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Worktree
Router->>StatusUseCase: execute(Worktree, signal)
StatusUseCase->>Worktree: getStatus(signal)
Worktree->>Runtime: getStatus(executionContext, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: getStatus(executionContext, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: clean status and stash list
Runtime-->>Worktree: clean status and stash list
Worktree-->>StatusUseCase: clean status and stash list
StatusUseCase-->>Router: clean status and stash list
Router-->>App: changes/statusResponse(requestId, status)
